<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WorldCashFit — CRM и мобильное приложение для фитнес-клубов и студий</title>
    <meta name="description" content="WorldCashFit: учётная система, CRM, мобильное приложение клиента и тренера, онлайн-запись, онлайн-оплата и аналитика для фитнес-клубов, студий йоги, танцев, единоборств и спорта.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #07091a;
            --bg-soft: #0e1430;
            --bg-card: #121a3a;
            --bg-card-2: #18204a;
            --text: #f1f4ff;
            --muted: #aab3d8;
            --primary: #5a8cff;
            --primary-2: #7aa6ff;
            --primary-hover: #3f77ff;
            --accent: #21d4a1;
            --accent-2: #ffb547;
            --danger: #ff5d6c;
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
            --border-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            --shadow: 0 30px 60px -20px rgba(7, 9, 26, 0.7);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Manrope", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg);
            line-height: 1.55;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        a { color: var(--primary-2); text-decoration: none; }

        img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 0.6em; }
        h1 { font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.4vw, 3.6rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        h2 { font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
        h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
        p { margin: 0 0 1em; }

        .container {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 2rem));
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            background: rgba(7, 9, 26, 0.85);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.9rem 0;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .logo-mark {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a8cff, #21d4a1);
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            color: #0a0d1f;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.4rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .nav a {
            color: var(--muted);
            transition: color 0.15s ease;
        }

        .nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }

        .header-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.45rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.78rem 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.18s ease;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #4d7bf0);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -10px rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.7);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 16px 28px -10px rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.85); }

        .btn-accent {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #1ab98c);
            color: #04261c;
        }

        .btn-accent:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

        .btn-ghost {
            color: var(--text);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); }

        .btn-lg { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; font-size: 1rem; border-radius: 14px; }

        /* HERO */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: -20% -10% auto -10%;
            height: 70%;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.45), transparent 45%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 75% 30%, rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.35), transparent 45%);
            filter: blur(30px);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .badge-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
            background: rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.12);
            color: #6ce0bd;
            border: 1px solid rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.3);
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .lead {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 56ch;
            margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.7rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .hero-stat {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
        }

        .hero-stat strong { display: block; font-size: 1.45rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .hero-stat span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

        /* Phone mockup (SVG-based illustration) */
        .hero-visual {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 480px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .phone {
            position: relative;
            width: 280px;
            height: 560px;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a2350, #0d1230);
            border: 6px solid #2a3470;
            border-radius: 42px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .phone::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 12px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 90px;
            height: 22px;
            background: #07091a;
            border-radius: 0 0 14px 14px;
        }

        .phone-screen {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 14px;
            border-radius: 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0c1130 0%, #131a3f 100%);
            padding: 38px 18px 18px;
            color: #f1f4ff;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
        }

        .phone-screen h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .phone-screen .ph-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        .ph-tag {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: #6ce0bd;
            background: rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.12);
            padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        .ph-btn {
            margin-top: 0.7rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #4d7bf0);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .floating-card {
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.7rem;
        }

        .fc-1 { top: 12%; left: -2%; }
        .fc-2 { bottom: 10%; right: -4%; }

        .fc-icon {
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: grid; place-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .fc-icon.green { background: rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.18); color: #6ce0bd; }
        .fc-icon.blue { background: rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.18); color: var(--primary-2); }

        /* Trust strip */
        .trust {
            padding: 2rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
        }

        .trust-title {
            color: var(--muted);
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .trust-logos {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .trust-logo {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-weight: 800;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.7rem 0.4rem;
        }

        /* Sections */
        section.block {
            padding: 4.5rem 0;
        }

        .section-head {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.4rem;
        }

        .section-head p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        /* Industries */
        .industries {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 0.85rem;
        }

        .industry {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            align-items: center;
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .industry:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--border-strong); }

        .industry-icon {
            width: 42px; height: 42px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: grid; place-items: center;
            background: rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.15);
            color: var(--primary-2);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .industry strong { display: block; }
        .industry span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .feature {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 1.4rem;
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .feature:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 48px; height: 48px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: grid; place-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.2), rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.15));
            color: var(--primary-2);
        }

        .feature p { color: var(--muted); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }

        /* Apps showcase */
        .apps {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .apps.reverse { direction: rtl; }
        .apps.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }

        .apps-info ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 1rem 0 1.4rem;
        }

        .apps-info li {
            position: relative;
            padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.7rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .apps-info li::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0.85rem;
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .apps-mock {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.12), rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.06));
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 2rem;
            min-height: 380px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
        }

        /* Numbers */
        .numbers {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #131b46, #0c1133);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .num-value {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #aab3d8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .numbers small { display: block; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.4rem; }

        /* Testimonials */
        .reviews {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .review {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 1.4rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .review-text {
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 0.97rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .review-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.7rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-top: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .review-avatar {
            width: 42px; height: 42px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: grid; place-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a8cff, #21d4a1);
            color: #04261c;
            font-weight: 800;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .review-author strong { display: block; }
        .review-author span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

        /* Pricing */
        .pricing {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .price-card {
            position: relative;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 1.6rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .price-card.featured {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #18225a, #131a3f);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -25px rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .price-card .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -12px; right: 16px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #04261c;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        .price-name { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
        .price-value {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0.4rem 0 0.1rem;
        }

        .price-value small { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; }

        .price-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 1rem 0 1.4rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        .price-list li {
            padding: 0.4rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .price-list li::before {
            content: "✓";
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* FAQ */
        .faq {
            max-width: 820px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        details.q {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }

        details.q[open] { border-color: var(--border-strong); }

        details.q summary {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        details.q summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
        details.q summary::after {
            content: "+";
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        details.q[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }

        details.q p {
            margin: 0.7rem 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        /* CTA */
        .cta-block {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a235a 0%, #102050 60%, #0a1133 100%);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 2.6rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-block::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(90, 140, 255, 0.4), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(33, 212, 161, 0.3), transparent 40%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .cta-block > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

        .cta-block h2 { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
        .cta-block p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.4rem; max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

        .cta-actions { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.7rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

        /* Form */
        .form-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 1.8rem;
        }

        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .form-grid .full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

        .field label {
            display: block;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .field input, .field textarea, .field select {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: 0.15s;
        }

        .field input:focus, .field textarea:focus, .field select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer.foot {
            padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .foot-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .foot h5 {
            color: var(--text);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
        }

        .foot a { display: block; color: var(--muted); padding: 0.2rem 0; }
        .foot a:hover { color: var(--text); }

        .foot-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-top: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
            .nav { display: none; }
            .hero-grid, .apps, .features, .industries, .pricing, .reviews, .numbers, .foot-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .hero-grid { gap: 1.6rem; }
            .hero-visual { min-height: 420px; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .hero-grid, .apps, .features, .industries, .pricing, .reviews, .form-grid, .foot-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .numbers { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .trust-logos { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
            .hero { padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
            section.block { padding: 3rem 0; }
            .floating-card { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
            <span class="logo-mark">W</span>
            <span>WorldCashFit</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav">
            <a href="#features">Возможности</a>
            <a href="#apps">Приложения</a>
            <a href="#pricing">Тарифы</a>
            <a href="#reviews">Отзывы</a>
            <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="header-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Демо бесплатно</a>
            <a href="{{ admin_url }}" class="btn btn-primary">Войти в админку</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main>
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
            <div>
                <span class="badge-pill">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                    14 дней демо. Без карты. Без обязательств
                </span>
                <h1>CRM, мобильное приложение и онлайн-запись для фитнес-клубов</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    WorldCashFit — единая платформа: учёт клиентов и абонементов, продажи, оплата онлайн,
                    приложение клиента и тренера, аналитика по выручке и загрузке. Запускайте за 1 день, экономьте на администраторах,
